data.description: Welcome Home! Lovely, exquisite & charming 3 bedroom, 1 bath home with tremendous interior updates is polished & move-in-ready! Enjoy wonderful exterior with lush front lawn, traditional red-brick siding, spacious carport with work shed,  RV parking with new side gate access & all new white vinyl exterior fencing! The backyard is newly graded with open stone patio & tremendous space for your enjoyment & blank canvas for your dream yard! The interior of the home features all new Life-proof Luxury Vinyl flooring & even new subfloors, all new interior paint, freshly updated baseboards, & absolutely stunning kitchen! The kitchen is seated in the heart of the home with beautiful quartz countertops, new white cabinetry, new stainless pulls, newer stainless appliances & lovely dining area. Enjoy elite caliber quality bedrooms with updated ceiling fans, can lighting overhead, updated closet doors and finely sanded & newly refined textured walls. The full bathroom features new hardwood vanity with marble top, new vanity mirror, new modern vanity lighting & white tile surround in shower/tub combo. The convenient laundry room is spacious and provides easy access outside to your spacious backyard! Enjoy newer swamp cooler, hot water heater and furnace all updated in 2019 & energy efficient dual pane white vinyl windows. Move into your new home with confidence which has been greatly loved and cared for. Fantastic home! Home sweet home! Seller installing all new black asphalt composition roof will be completed next week.
